nother to compassion.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["transgressed","decreed","judged"],"pos":"V","lemma":"آمَنَ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"āmanū"},{"id":"ac-90:18:1","surahNum":90,"ayahNum":18,"wordNum":1,"arabic":"ذا","targetTranslation":"those (far away) (subject of أَصْحٰبُ)","ayahArabic":"أُو۟لٰٓئِكَ أَصْحٰبُ ٱلْمَيْمَنَةِ","ayahEnglish":"Those are the companions of the right.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["The scales","A covenant","The angels"],"pos":"N","lemma":"ذا","tier":"q100","transliteration":"ulāika"},{"id":"ac-90:18:2","surahNum":90,"ayahNum":18,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"أَصْحاب","targetTranslation":"companions (as the doers/subjects of ٱلْمَيْمَنَةِ)","ayahArabic":"أُو۟لٰٓئِكَ أَصْحٰبُ ٱلْمَيْمَنَةِ","ayahEnglish":"Those are the companions of the right.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["the signs","the gardens","the mountains"],"pos":"N","lemma":"أَصْحاب","tier":"q300","transliteration":"aṣḥābu"},{"id":"ac-90:19:2","surahNum":90,"ayahNum":19,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","targetTranslation":"they rejected/denied (referring to those who - الَّذِينَ)","ayahArabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ بِـَٔايٰتِنَا هُمْ أَصْحٰبُ ٱلْمَشْـَٔمَةِ","ayahEnglish":"But they who disbelieved in Our signs - those are the companions of the left.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he measured","he hastened","he judged"],"pos":"V","lemma":"كَفَرَ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"kafarū"},{"id":"ac-90:19:4","surahNum":90,"ayahNum":19,"wordNum":4,"arabic":"هُمْ","targetTranslation":"they/them (subject of أَصْحٰبُ)","ayahArabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ بِـَٔايٰتِنَا هُمْ أَصْحٰبُ ٱلْمَشْـَٔمَةِ","ayahEnglish":"But they who disbelieved in Our signs - those are the companions of the left.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["submitted","abandoned","be opened"],"pos":"N","lemma":"هُمْ","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"hum"},{"id":"ac-90:19:5","surahNum":90,"ayahNum":19,"wordNum":5,"arabic":"أَصْحاب","targetTranslation":"companions (subject of هُمْ)","ayahArabic":"وَٱلَّذ